  <abstract>
    <para>
      Qlustar is a complete Linux distribution based on Debian/Ubuntu. Its main purpose is to
      provide an Operating System (OS) that simplifies the setup, administration, monitoring
      and general use of HPC, Storage and Virtualization/Cloud Linux clusters. Hence we call
      Qlustar a <emphasis>Cluster OS</emphasis>.
    </para>
